==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stipend
<hw>Sti"pend</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>stipendium</ets>; <ets>stips</ets>, gen. <ets>stipis</ets>, a gift,
donation, given in small coin + <ets>pendere</ets> to weigh or pay
out.]</ety> <def>Settled pay or compensation for services, whether paid
daily, monthly, or annually.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stipend</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Stipend
<hw>Sti"pend</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To pay by settled wages.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stipendiarian</ent>⟦br⟧
